1
00:01:49,370 --> 00:01:54,979
[A Dream Within A Dream]

2
00:01:55,009 --> 00:01:57,910
[Episode 15]

3
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,350
I'm Song Yimeng.

4
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,940
Greetings, Your Majesty.

5
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:09,400
Kneel.

6
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:14,080
It's late,

7
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,190
and I'm tired.

8
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:18,320
So I won't beat around the bush.

9
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,550
You're already engaged,

10
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:23,750
yet you're tangled up with a prince,

11
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:27,120
even pitting Rui and Heng
against each other.

12
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:28,650
Tell me.

13
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:31,750
What exactly are you
and your family plotting?

14
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:33,230
Your Majesty,

15
00:02:34,790 --> 00:02:36,450
please don't misunderstand.

16
00:02:36,770 --> 00:02:39,000
My father raised me to steer clear

17
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,280
of political factions.

18
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,600
My engagement to Chu Guihong

19
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:45,240
was arranged years ago.

20
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,890
The rumors about the Seventh Prince and me

21
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,560
are completely baseless.

22
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,620
[Exceptional Love]

23
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,450
You're a woman,

24
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:58,540
and women should have womanly virtues.

25
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,150
Since you're engaged,

26
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,400
you should

27
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,550
stay at home,

28
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,630
do some embroidery,

29
00:03:04,630 --> 00:03:06,080
and read a book or two.

30
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,590
You dressed to the nines

31
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,060
for the fancy banquet in the capital.

32
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:16,240
You just wanted
to attract attention, didn't you?

33
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,970
Not everything that goes wrong

34
00:03:20,410 --> 00:03:22,280
is a woman's fault.

35
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:25,870
What a sharp tongue!

36
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,680
Today, two princes drew swords
against each other

37
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,280
all because of you.

38
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,120
Everyone saw it,

39
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:37,079
and you're still trying to deny it.

40
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,560
Are you trying to start

41
00:03:39,579 --> 00:03:41,560
a war between the two princes?

42
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,030
Take her away

43
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,360
and give her 20 strokes.

44
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:50,000
Your Majesty.

45
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:50,840
Your Majesty!

46
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,560
Hold on!

47
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,740
Your Highness,

48
00:03:54,770 --> 00:03:56,079
what are you doing

49
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:58,010
barging into the Imperial Study?

50
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,600
Your Majesty,

51
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,170
everything that happened

52
00:04:03,170 --> 00:04:04,800
was entirely my fault.

53
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,030
I knew

54
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,730
she was already engaged,

55
00:04:07,730 --> 00:04:09,060
but I still pursued her.

56
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,950
I was the one
who had those books made

57
00:04:11,950 --> 00:04:13,360
and circulated.

58
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,850
I also begged Mother

59
00:04:14,850 --> 00:04:16,310
to issue a marriage decree

60
00:04:16,329 --> 00:04:17,130
for us.

61
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,870
I didn't set you up.

62
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:22,770
The marriage decree came from Mother.

63
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:24,370
What's that got to do with me?

64
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:29,000
None of this
has anything to do with Miss Song.

65
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:29,950
Your Majesty,

66
00:04:30,190 --> 00:04:31,650
please punish me instead.

67
00:04:32,470 --> 00:04:33,310
Very well.

68
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:35,430
In these 28 years,

69
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,560
my seventh son

70
00:04:37,730 --> 00:04:39,000
has never

71
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,140
made a single mistake—

72
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:41,870
flawless in every way,

73
00:04:41,900 --> 00:04:42,990
not once

74
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:45,220
giving anyone anything to use against him.

75
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:48,020
Yet now here you are,
kneeling and admitting guilt

76
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:50,310
all for the sake of a woman.

77
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,120
Fine.

78
00:04:52,690 --> 00:04:54,120
Then tell me.

79
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:56,270
Aside from the Song family behind her,

80
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:58,070
what makes her so special?

81
00:05:01,490 --> 00:05:03,630
Your Majesty,
you loved the late Empress

82
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:05,890
not because of the Chu family behind her.

83
00:05:06,090 --> 00:05:07,680
How dare you speak out of turn

84
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,920
about the Emperor?

85
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,560
Listen,

86
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:13,070
her engagement was arranged long ago.

87
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,810
It cannot be changed!

88
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:16,630
Be it ruler or subject,

89
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,480
in this world,

90
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,420
everyone must follow the rules.

91
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:20,830
I wouldn't dare to break the rules.

92
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:21,950
You wouldn't dare?

93
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,950
You drew your sword against Rui

94
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:25,510
at the musical banquet.

95
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,420
How was that following the rules?

96
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:35,230
It was because

97
00:05:35,260 --> 00:05:36,430
he insulted the Gao family

98
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:37,590
and my mother.

99
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:38,800
The law of Great Jing makes it clear:

100
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,120
those who turn on their own kin

101
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,980
must be imprisoned and executed.

102
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:47,120
But today,

103
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:48,700
I won't kill you.

104
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:52,380
The hand you used

105
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:54,600
to dislocate Rui's arm—

106
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,950
cut it off.

107
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,510
What?

108
00:06:09,490 --> 00:06:10,720
You want to

109
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,040
defy my order?

110
00:06:18,490 --> 00:06:20,610
This is treason!

111
00:06:32,530 --> 00:06:33,420
Your Majesty,

112
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,290
everything that happened today

113
00:06:36,290 --> 00:06:37,540
was my fault.

114
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,930
His Highness had nothing to do with it.

115
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,240
Besides,

116
00:06:41,570 --> 00:06:44,700
the Eighteenth Prince
also wounded the Seventh Prince.

117
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,920
What's this?

118
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:55,830
You're a prince,

119
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:58,400
and now you're scared

120
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:01,870
and need a woman to plead for you?

121
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,720
Your Majesty,

122
00:07:14,970 --> 00:07:15,960
as you wish.

123
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,820
Your Highness.

124
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:28,390
[Exceptional Love]

125
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:32,690
Your Highness!

126
00:07:55,100 --> 00:07:56,520
No, Your Highness!

127
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,820
I was just joking.

128
00:08:11,490 --> 00:08:12,890
Why take it so seriously?

129
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:24,850
Or do you want the whole world

130
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:27,850
to call me a cruel tyrant
who maimed his own son?

131
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,510
I…

132
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,049
I wouldn't dare.

133
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,520
Your Majesty.

134
00:08:42,909 --> 00:08:43,919
Your Majesty,

135
00:08:43,950 --> 00:08:46,130
the Noble Consort fainted in her chambers.

136
00:08:46,130 --> 00:08:47,560
She's delirious

137
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,960
and keeps calling for

138
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:51,390
the Seventh Prince and Miss Song.

139
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,520
Your Majesty,

140
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,630
I'll answer for this another day

141
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:09,090
and accept
whatever punishment you see fit.

142
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,870
But now,

143
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:11,810
my mother has suddenly collapsed.

144
00:09:11,810 --> 00:09:13,070
Please, Your Majesty,

145
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:14,720
let me go to her.

146
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:18,110
Get lost.

147
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,840
Thank you, Your Majesty.

148
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:26,470
I shall take my leave.

149
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:33,000
Your Highness,

150
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,360
please go and see her.

151
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:35,320
Mother!

152
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,420
Your Highness.

153
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:38,120
Mother!

154
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:44,240
What's this?

155
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,800
Her Ladyship said

156
00:09:56,830 --> 00:09:59,730
Your Highness and Miss Song
should go to bed.

157
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,370
Open the door!

158
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:07,230
My Lady,

159
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:09,150
how did it go?

160
00:10:09,390 --> 00:10:10,340
My Lady,

161
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:12,320
they didn't let go

162
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:15,250
of each other's hands the whole way.

163
00:10:18,250 --> 00:10:19,370
Heng.

164
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:20,440
I've done

165
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,960
all I can for you.

166
00:10:21,980 --> 00:10:23,020
The rest

167
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:25,050
is up to you.

168
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,510
Master.

169
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:34,120
Where is she?

170
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,630
The palace attendants said

171
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:37,080
Her Ladyship summoned Miss Song

172
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:37,910
midway.

173
00:10:39,730 --> 00:10:40,670
Then send someone

174
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:42,670
to inquire
at Noble Consort Gao's place.

175
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:44,030
I did.

176
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,590
The maids there said

177
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,910
Miss Song had already left the palace

178
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:47,910
and gone home.

179
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,000
Master,

180
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,280
that's impossible.

181
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:51,480
If she had really gone home,

182
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,120
Zhixia would've sent word.

183
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:53,910
She…

184
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:54,440
she…

185
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:56,080
she must still be in the palace.

186
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,600
Something must've happened.

187
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,880
Don't panic.

188
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:01,920
No one enters the palace
at night unless summoned.

189
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:03,250
Let's wait a bit longer.

190
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,720
Just as I thought.

191
00:11:24,630 --> 00:11:26,030
Don't waste your energy.

192
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:27,630
This is Her Ladyship's plan.

193
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:30,350
What do you mean?

194
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,910
A classic costume-drama scene.

195
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:33,720
The male and female leads

196
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,910
end up stuck in a room,

197
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:35,910
forced to bond.

198
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:38,200
Since Her Ladyship came up with this idea,

199
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,320
there's no way

200
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:41,240
we're getting out of here tonight.

201
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,440
How do you know that?

202
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,670
Of course I know.

203
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,160
It's a classic scene.

204
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,240
I've played it out

205
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,770
more times than I can count.

206
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:49,440
You know what?

207
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,170
We might as well just go with it.

208
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,000
Wait.

209
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,130
You're a young lady…

210
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,910
alone in a room with a man.

211
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:59,040
Shouldn't you behave with propriety?

212
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:00,870
I…

213
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:01,960
It's too tight.

214
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:04,030
What's wrong with
making myself more comfortable?

215
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:05,150
Why are you so nervous?

216
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:05,910
I...

217
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:13,390
You didn't seem this nervous

218
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:14,910
when you spread the rumors.

219
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:17,230
Now you're afraid
I'll take advantage of you?

220
00:12:17,230 --> 00:12:18,430
Why would I be afraid?

221
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:21,080
What do I even have
for you to take advantage of?

222
00:12:25,990 --> 00:12:28,210
Then explain this—

223
00:12:29,130 --> 00:12:32,000
what was that marriage decree
from Her Ladyship all about?

224
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,440
And just now, in front of the Emperor,

225
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:35,030
you took all the blame for me.

226
00:12:35,030 --> 00:12:36,760
What was that supposed to mean?

227
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:37,670
Also,

228
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,640
I really want to know—

229
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,960
if His Majesty
hadn't stopped you just now,

230
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:46,070
would you really have cut off your hand?

231
00:12:51,630 --> 00:12:52,770
I was just gambling,

232
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:55,460
like I've been doing

233
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:56,720
all my life.

234
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,890
Gambling that if I obey and behave,

235
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,720
I'll be let off one more time.

236
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:11,600
Well then.

237
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:13,910
Looks like

238
00:13:14,610 --> 00:13:16,860
the fake couple in "Exceptional Love"

239
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:19,340
has made its way to the Emperor.

240
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,790
I gotta say, you're pretty bold,

241
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:24,910
daring to touch the Emperor's sore spot.

242
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:25,720
I've already told you,

243
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,580
this whole thing wasn't my doing.

244
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,910
You think I'm dumb enough

245
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:30,630
to risk being accused of treason

246
00:13:30,630 --> 00:13:31,720
just to…

247
00:13:32,140 --> 00:13:33,800
to play a fake couple with you?

248
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:35,200
Are you out of your mind?

249
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,430
That does sound absurd.

250
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,120
Fair point.

251
00:13:44,690 --> 00:13:46,230
So you saved me

252
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:48,020
just because of...

253
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,240
Don't think I don't know

254
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,550
why you helped me.

255
00:13:57,550 --> 00:13:58,950
You're overthinking it.

256
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,100
I helped you

257
00:14:00,270 --> 00:14:01,080
only because of

258
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,670
the rules you mentioned.

259
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,750
The rule that when the female lead

260
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:09,010
is in danger, the male lead must save her.

261
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:20,060
Miss Song, you're really clever.

262
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,440
Brilliant, even.

263
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,030
You…

264
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:33,090
What are you doing?

265
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,100
What do you think I'm doing?

266
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:35,870
Going to sleep.

267
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:36,550
It's already 10 PM.

268
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:38,280
You want me to stay up all night?

269
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:40,790
Does a workaholic
like you even need sleep?

270
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:41,870
Even the King of Hell

271
00:14:41,870 --> 00:14:43,270
has to sleep.

272
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:44,840
But this place is so big.

273
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:45,720
Why do you have to

274
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,930
sleep on the bed?

275
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:47,720
Well, if not here,

276
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,670
am I s-supposed to

277
00:14:48,670 --> 00:14:49,730
sleep on the floor?

278
00:14:49,790 --> 00:14:50,600
But if you sleep here,

279
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:51,440
where am I supposed to sleep?

280
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,910
Wherever you want.

281
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:55,030
Didn't you just tell me

282
00:14:55,670 --> 00:14:56,560
to go with

283
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:57,910
the flow?

284
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:03,720
You…

285
00:15:06,580 --> 00:15:11,340
[Seventh Prince's Mansion]

286
00:15:08,550 --> 00:15:09,550
Guard the mansion.

287
00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:11,350
I'll go bring His Highness back!

288
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:17,930
[Seventh Prince's Mansion]

289
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:18,960
General Chu.

290
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,020
Guard the mansion.

291
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,540
I'll go bring Yimeng back.

292
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:26,480
[Qianyu Mansion]

293
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,910
You all head back first.

