619
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:48,020
All I've ever wanted

620
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:50,380
is for Heng to be safe and happy.

621
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:52,600
But what about you?

622
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:54,690
What have you done?

623
